@10   = ~Escape from this place is possible, but only for those who prove their worthiness through intellect and insight. Solve the riddles laid before you, and the path to freedom shall reveal itself. But be warned, the journey ahead is perilous, and the price of failure is steep.~
@11   = ~Seek the answers, let wisdom guide,
Through the maze where minds collide.
Fail the test, and danger nears,
In this space of doubts and fears.~
@12   = ~So listen carefully and answer my question correctly...~
@13   = ~"I am the shadow in the scholar's light,
The empty page in the book of might.
Where wisdom fades into the night,
And certainty is lost from sight.
In me, no secrets will you find,
No truths to seek, no lore to bind.
What am I, that leaves you blind,
A desert for the seeking mind?"~
