@24   = ~"I twist the past with silent ease,
Infecting thoughts like a disease.
Memories that once did please,
Now turned to dark fantasies.
I'm not what was, but what you fear,
A whisper false, yet sounds so clear.
What am I, that draws near,
The distortion of what you hold dear?"~
